HEADWORD: Worldliness
<hw>World"li*ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of
being worldly; a predominant passion for obtaining the good things of
this life; covetousness; addictedness to gain and temporal enjoyments;
worldly-mindedness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Worldling</ent>⟦br⟧
